Tga '''Tarudant''' (s [[Tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]]: ⵜⴰⵔⵓⴷⴰⵏ) yat tiɣrmt illan ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]] ɣ uzaɣar n [[Sus]] ɣ iffus n tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]].

Ar ittini liḥṣa lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2004 mas tiɣrmt ad zdɣn gis kra n 80 149 imzdaɣ<ref>[http://rgphentableaux.hcp.ma/ GPH 2014 - Site HCP]</ref>. 

Tlla tiɣrmt ad ɣ ngr [[Agadir]] d [[Warzazat]], tili ɣ iffus n [[Mrrakc]]. Illa mad ittinin i tarudant mas tga "Jddas n Mrrakc" acku trwas t nit mac tmẓẓiy fllas.

==Aẓur n yism==

Ur illi kra n aẓur iṣḥan i wawal ad n "Tarudant". Llan kigan n iẓuran d ku-yan d may-ttini aylliɣ ur sul nssn manta gisn ay ṣḥan.
Aẓur nna akk gisn ittawssan iga tt mas ism ad n "Tarudant" ikka d "Tarwa ddant". Xtad s yixf nns iɣ fllas sawln middn ar tbdarn lqist n kra n tazzanin yiwitn wasif lliɣ yut yat twal lfayaḍan tiɣrmt ad ɣ mayad izrin, ɣayn ad yujjan innasn ad tg taɣuyyit tlhu : "Tarwa ddant".
